import React from 'react' import './Abouttheday.css'; const Abouttheday = () => { return (
About the day
Timings will be confirmed closer to the date.



  • Will there be parking available?
  • Yes, you can park at the venue
  • How do I get from the station?
  • There is a taxi rank at the station or Uber can be used.
  • Can I take pictures during the ceremony?
  • We kindly ask for no photos during the ceremony.
  • What is the dress code?
  • Smart Formal, no jeans, no trainers
  • Are Children allowed at the wedding?
  • Yes, all children are welcome at the ceremony & reception
) } export default Abouttheday
